Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.67,0:00:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到羅德斯島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.80,0:00:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼緊接著\N就請觀賞第二部份吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.67,0:00:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,~歡迎來到羅德斯島~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.65,0:00:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是史派克…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.29,0:00:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是佛雷姆的騎士，史派克啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.49,0:00:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本應該是那樣的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.11,0:00:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在幹什麼呀，史派克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.93,0:00:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要丟下你不管囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.67,0:00:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好，馬上就去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.07,0:00:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.47,0:00:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騎士資格考試的補考\N竟然只是送餅乾而已…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.01,0:00:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼啊，史派克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.61,0:00:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,護衛也是騎士重要的任務喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.78,0:00:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話是這樣沒錯啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.67,0:00:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是到底有誰會要搶餅乾呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.39,0:00:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種護衛怎麼看都不像是考試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.46,0:00:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?哇…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.79,0:00:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史派克!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.06,0:00:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差點以為自己死定了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.13,0:01:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈…沒想到有護衛在旁\N才讓妳撿回一條命哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.84,0:01:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.24,0:01:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等妳很久了，妮絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.97,0:01:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.11,0:01:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡甜食的暗妖精!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.55,0:01:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗妖精?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.48,0:01:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說瑪法神官所烤的餅乾\N是頂尖的美味…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.32,0:01:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是乖乖地把餅乾交給我吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.72,0:01:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.23,0:01:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太過份了，沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.79,0:01:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，還好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.46,0:01:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等!等等，等等，等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.93,0:01:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好聽完人家說話啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.17,0:01:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若敢輕視本大爺\N就讓你知道厲害!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.77,0:01:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮絲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.81,0:01:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.28,0:01:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝，龍寶寶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.71,0:01:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來，我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.52,0:01:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何我對往後的旅程\N感到非常不安…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.73,0:01:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得再看哦
